              </DEFINITION>
            </ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-STRING>
            <ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-STRING THE-VALUE="If the message receive operation times out before a message becomes available, the Zephyr RTOS shall return an appropriate timeout error code to the receiving thread.">
