              </DEFINITION>
            </ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-STRING>
            <ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-STRING THE-VALUE="The Zephyr RTOS shall handle message exchange via a mailbox object non-anonymously, allowing both the sending and receiving threads to know the identity of the other thread.">
