              </DEFINITION>
            </ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-STRING>
            <ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-STRING THE-VALUE="As a Zephyr RTOS developer, I want the system to validate my inputs and return errors rather than crash when I provide invalid parameters so that I can develop more robust applications.">
