              </DEFINITION>
            </ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-STRING>
            <ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-STRING THE-VALUE="As a Zephyr RTOS user I want to be able to request read-only or read-write access to a dedicated memory area/pool during runtime.">
