              </DEFINITION>
            </ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-STRING>
            <ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-STRING THE-VALUE="The Zephyr RTOS shall provide a communication primitive that allows threads to exchange messages of varying sizes asynchronously or synchronously.">
